stylometry: The concept of sensitivity analysis is to find out how changing your inputs certain inputs would effect and change the outputs based on the input change. It shows you how changing an input could give you better optimization and it is important because it can show you decisions you might be able to make to save on costs or make more profit. SolverTable is the solver add-in that is used to perform the sensitivity analysis by solving for all the possible new outputs given a different input.
